e1.jpeg&h=a76cb460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">馬刺成員 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPop [廢老pop 波波]   /  TD<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMurray [Murray 揸ass 屎忽鬼  DJ] /  Patty [毛巾]<br />\n<br />\nWhite [小白 白帝 少主] /  Forbes [冰科 聖城咖哩] /  Marco [意粉]  /  Walker [行路草 芹菜] / Weatherspoon [天氣羹]<br />\n<br />\nDeMar [DDR] / DeMarre /Johnson [babyruss]<br />\n<br />\nGay /   Samanic [三文治] / Tyles<br />\n<br />\nAldridge [LMA] /Poeltl [白腸]  / Eubanks [歐銀] / Metu [美圖]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">垃圾刺圍爐po守則 :<br />\n<br />\n1.魚腩最忌有自信<br />\n<br />\n2.垃圾係唔屌唔得嘅，垃圾無一個讚得<br />\n<br />\n3.永遠唔好存有贏波希望去睇垃圾廁既波<br />\n<br />\n4.平安鐘是必須<br />\n<br />\n5.倒水只會遲到不會缺席<br />\n<br />\n6.三分射手們骰仔中六先入<br />\n<br />\n7.廢過tank隊，輸30分係基本</span><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSoxvg8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSoxvg8.gif&h=145b3c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">馬巴</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/o2hUGfA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2hUGfA.gif&h=b48bb066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開PO專用  <a href=\"https://goo.gl/a7zBiA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fa7zBiA&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=b60f2f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/a7zBiA</a>"},{"pid":"4ced30d2d9b996ebd870555e1c97018f5f0e8324","tid":1686203,"uid":